# === GALA build artifacts ===
# Local analysis cache written by `gala build` / `gala test`. (Build
# workspaces and the transpiled .gen.go output live globally under ~/.gala.)
.gala/
# Transpiled Go output, if it ever leaks into the source tree.
*.gen.go
# Built binaries from `gala build`.
*.exe

# === Bazel ===
/bazel-*

# === JetBrains IDEs ===
.idea/

# === macOS ===
.DS_Store
